										What could be more elegant and easier to wear than <strong>Diamond Studs</strong>?
									</span>
									<ul class="top5">
										<li>@Html.RouteLink("18K Gold Diamonds Studs", "Tabs", new RouteValueDictionary()
																	 {
																		 {"tabkey", "diamond-rings"},
																		 {"tabid", "diamond-studs"},
																		 {"page", 1},
																	 }) </li>
										<li>@Html.RouteLink("Round Diamonds Studs", "Tabs", new RouteValueDictionary()
																	 {
																		 {"tabkey", "diamond-rings"},
																		 {"tabid", "diamond-studs"},
